OL,3,CTrump confirms he will sue the BBC
OL,4,C'between $1bn and $5bn'
OL,6,FPresident Trump confirmed on Friday
OL,7,Fthat he still intends to take legal
OL,8,Faction against BBC over how his speech
OL,9,Fwas edited by Panorama.
OL,11,F"We'll sue them from $1bn to $5bn,
OL,12,Fprobably sometime next week," he told
OL,13,Freporters on board Air Force One.
OL,15,F"We have to do it, they've even
OL,16,Fadmitted that they cheated. Not that
OL,17,Fthey couldn't have not done that. They
OL,18,Fcheated. They changed the words coming
OL,19,Fout of my mouth," he said.
