OL,6,FPresident Trump said he had not spoken
OL,7,Fwith Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fyet but planned to do so over the
OL,9,Fweekend.
OL,11,FHe told reporters "the people of the
OL,12,FUK are very angry about what
OL,13,Fhappened...because it shows the BBC is
OL,14,Ffake news".
OL,16,FThis comes after the BBC apologised to
OL,17,FTrump after splicing two clips
OL,18,Ftogether from a speech he delivered
OL,19,Ffor an episode of Panorama - as the
OL,20,Fbroadcaster was accused of another
OL,21,Fmisleading edit.
