OL,6,FWhen asked by GB News' Bev Turner
OL,7,Fduring a sit-down interview whether he
OL,8,Fwould seek compensation, President
OL,9,FTrump told Turner: "I think I have an
OL,10,Fobligation to do it."
OL,12,F"I'm not looking to get into lawsuits,
OL,13,Fbut I think I have an obligation to do
OL,14,Fit.
OL,16,F"This was so egregious if you don't.
OL,17,FYou don't stop it from happening again
OL,18,Fwith other people."
