OL,6,FThe documentary featured two clips
OL,7,Ffrom a speech made by President Trump
OL,8,Fon January 6 2021 which were
OL,9,Fselectively edited together,
OL,10,Freportedly making it appear that he
OL,11,Fwas encouraging his supporters to riot.
OL,13,FEarlier this week Trump's lawyers
OL,14,Fthreatened to sue the BBC for $1bn in
OL,15,Fdamages unless the corporation issued
OL,16,Fa retraction, apologised and
OL,17,Fcompensated him.
