OL,3,CTrump confirms he will sue the BBC
OL,4,C'between $1bn and $5bn'
OL,6,FThe backlash led to the resignations
OL,7,Fboth BBC director-general Tim Davie
OL,8,Fand BBC News chief executive Deborah
OL,9,FTurness from their roles.
OL,11,FTrump's lawyers had given the BBC a
OL,12,Fdeadline of 10pm on Friday 14 November
OL,13,Fto respond, which it did.
OL,15,FOn Thursday, the broadcaster
OL,16,Fofficially apologised to the US
OL,17,Fpresident and added that it was an
OL,18,F"error of judgement" and the programme
OL,19,Fwill "not be broadcast again in this
OL,20,Fform on any BBC platforms".
