OL,3,CTrump confirms he will sue the BBC
OL,4,C'between $1bn and $5bn'
OL,6,FTalking to GB News on Friday,
OL,7,FPresident Trump said "they wrote me a
OL,8,Fnice letter. We apologise. But when
OL,9,Fyou say it's unintentional, I guess if
OL,10,Fit's unintentional you don't apologise.
OL,12,F"I made a beautiful statement and they
OL,13,Fmade it into a not beautiful
OL,14,Fstatement."
OL,16,FThe BBC also said it was looking into
OL,17,Ffresh allegations, published in The
OL,18,FTelegraph, that its Newsnight show
OL,19,Falso selectively edited footage of the
OL,20,Fsame speech in a report broadcast in
OL,21,FJune 2022.
